topPRs.title: feat: add release configuration and workflows for automated publishing
topPRs.author: M4XGO
topPRs.body:
## WHY  : 
Adding a complete CI/CD workflow to the repository with the aim of publishing plugins on NPM. 
Created .release-please-manifest.json to define the release version.
Added release-please-config.json for release type and changelog configuration.
Implemented GitHub Actions workflows for automated NPM publishing and release management.

## How :
Using the precedent reusable-workflow I've made here : https://github.com/Sendo-labs/reusable-workflows/
